## Research Integration (from pre-researcher.out)

All 6 questions resolved:
| Q | Answer |
|---|---|
| Q1: Free stems URL | None (all require login). Programmatic fallback activated. |
| Q2: Second free song | Same — generate programmatically with different metadata. |
| Q3: MultiTracks UI | Horizontal channel strips, section chips top, transport pinned top, dark DAW. Confirms plan layout. |
| Q4: Loop Community UI | Same conventions; section markers, per-track mute/solo/volume; dark professional. Confirms. |
| Q5: Web Audio sample-lock | CONFIRMED. Same-frame `.start(currentTime)` = same 128-sample block = sample-locked all browsers. |
| Q6: Scheduler reference | Chris Wilson "A Tale of Two Clocks" — 25ms interval / 100ms lookahead. ~50 lines vanilla JS. |

