## Constraints + Quality Gates

- ≤12 src files (exact count above: 12).
- Build must complete in <3 min (`npm run build`).
- No console errors on first paint.
- All 9 pain points demonstrable in a single user session without explanation.
- No em/en dashes in any proposal prose.
- Design coherent, bespoke, not portfolio-look.
- Demo link in cover letter AND deck.
- Proposal explicitly answers all 4 application questions.

